## 🧑‍💻 Getting Started

### Prerequisites

* Node.js
* Java (JDK 17+)
* Python 3.x
* MySQL/PostgreSQL

---

### Installation

#### 1. Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo.git
cd your-repo
```

#### 2. Backend Setup (Spring Boot)

```bash
cd backend
./mvnw spring-boot:run
```

#### 3. Frontend Setup (React)

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
npm run dev
```

#### 4. AI Service (Flask)

```bash
cd ml-service
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

